</XX>
<CO>Amcor.
    North Broken Hill Peko.
    Reinson Goldfields.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>AUZ  Australia.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P2621 Paper Mills.
